<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Calamagrostis nutkaensis </i>sprouts easily after fire, and resident Native Americans regularly burned it prior to European management (Anderson 2005).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
			<td>Short (2-10 years)
				
